E Co group, which opens the possibility to change job, profession or industry all within one global organization.  Together, we are all innovators, pioneers and team players who are passionate about making payment solutions that millions of people depend on every day.                 Ready to start a new chapter with CPI?         Joining CPI is the start of your next career chapter that will create multiple great new experiences and opportunities.                Opportunities - U.S.A                             Opportunities - Rest of the World                                         Solutions      Cashless  Coin  Note  Pay Station  Tools        Markets      Financial Services  Gaming  Retail  Transport  Vending       About Us     What we do  Why CPI  Life at CPI  Contact Us  Crane Corporate       Quick Links     Home  News  Events  Case Studies  Testimonials  Legal                          © 2018 Crane Payment Innovations (CPI)     Policies  |  Terms and Conditions     Experience by            Login     Products     Support     Careers     Contact        